function validate(email) {
    var re = /^(([^<>()[\]\\.,;:\s@\"]+(\.[^<>()[\]\\.,;:\s@\"]+)*)|(\".+\"))@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\])|(([a-zA-Z\-0-9]+\.)+[a-zA-Z]{2,}))$/;
    return re.test(email);
}

var d=new Date();
var weekday=new Array("Pazar","Pazartesi","Salı","Çarşamba","Perşembe","Cuma","Cumartesi");
var saat = d.getHours();
if((saat >= 20) || (saat < 6)){
    b_text = "Bu Gece";
}else{
    b_text = "Bugün";
}

var thisDay = b_text;

$(".nextDay").html(nextDay);


function hava_durumu(cookie_gelen){
    if(cookie_gelen == null){
        cookie_gelen = 2344116;
        cookie_yap = 0;
    }else{cookie_yap = 1;}

    $(".havadurumu table").css('display','none');

    var degerler = {
        sehir: cookie_gelen
    };
    $.ajax({
        url: 'ajax.php',
        data: degerler,
        type: "POST",
        dataType: 'json',
        success: function(JSON){
            $(".bgn_d").html("&nbsp;"+JSON.sehir.bgn_d +"°");
            $(".bgn_y").html(JSON.sehir.bgn_y +"°");
            $(".yrn_d").html("&nbsp;"+JSON.sehir.yrn_b +"°");
            $(".yrn_y").html(JSON.sehir.yrn_y +"°");
            r_deger = (JSON.sehir.background1);
            ry_deger = (JSON.sehir.background2);
            $(".havadurumu table td.icon:eq(0)").attr('style','background-position: -'+r_deger+'px 50%');
            $(".havadurumu table td.icon:eq(1)").attr('style','background-position: -'+ry_deger+'px 50%');
            $(".havadurumu table").show();
            $(".havadurumu #veri_var").hide();
            $(".havadurumu .yukleniyor").css('display','none');
            if(cookie_yap != 0){
                document.cookie="sehir="+cookie_gelen+"; expires=Sun, 16 Oct 2039 15:57:02 GMT; path=/";
            }

        }
    });
}

    function parseParamsFromUrl() {
        var params = {};
        var parts = window.location.search.substr(1).split('\x26');
        for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {
            var keyValuePair = parts[i].split('=');
            var key = decodeURIComponent(keyValuePair[0]);
            params[key] = keyValuePair[1] ?
                    decodeURIComponent(keyValuePair[1].replace(/\+/g, ' ')) :
                    keyValuePair[1];
        }
        return params;
    }
